{"tid":1716114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【出去嘅手足入】進 攻 係 最 好 嘅 防 守","createTime":"2019-11-13T09:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T07:12:39.000Z","uid":198113,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"4a3dca003db87ffa8ac53b255eaaf8d23566a88b","tid":1716114,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:10:51.000Z","msg":"琴日中環有版比你地睇 只要人數一夠 向前進攻 班狗乜柒都唔夠膽做 淨係舉起支槍嚇下你哋 然後即刻開車走<br />\n<br />\n不過唔係立亂進攻  進攻前有以下前提<br />\n1.人數比例同班狗至少係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3:1</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.檢查手足們裝備<span style=\"color: gold;\">是否能夠應付催淚彈同橡膠子彈等等</span><br />\n<br />\n3.前線<span style=\"color: gold;\">是否真武勇</span>（唔係見狗就走嘅和理非）<br />\n<br />\n4.檢查清楚<span style=\"color: gold;\">附近係真係冇狗埋伏同支援</span>先好進攻<br />\n<br />\n5.一旦決定要進攻 就要<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一口氣衝或者行上去<br />\n千祈唔好向前行下又停下</span></strong></span> 咁樣只會令班狗有時間研究點樣對付你哋 所以一定要殺佢哋一個措手不及 唔比佢哋有時間反應<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6.<span style=\"color: gold;\">一切都要視乎當時環境同情況而決定</span><br />\n<br />\n香港人 報仇 再唔係一句口號 而係要行動 唔好再比班狗睇死我哋唔識進攻<br />\n<br />\n最後請各位安全至上 期待同你地喺煲底除罩相見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">如有更多建議 歡迎喺下邊提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"05a4ad9e75af4aa1de7b49f6fe4239a993781754","tid":1716114,"uid":198113,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"良好示範 請參考<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WaxEdj9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWaxEdj9.gif&h=a355f2d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/73nHVyw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F73nHVyw.gif&h=abb306b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fY1hKrS.g