只要人數一夠 向前進攻 班狗乜柒都唔夠膽做 淨係舉起支槍嚇下你哋 然後即刻開車走<br />\n<br />\n不過唔係立亂進攻  進攻前有以下前提<br />\n1.人數比例同班狗至少係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3:1</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.檢查手足們裝備<span style=\"color: gold;\">是否能夠應付催淚彈同橡膠子彈等等</span><br />\n<br />\n3.前線<span style=\"color: gold;\">是否真武勇</span>（唔係見狗就走嘅和理非）<br />\n<br />\n4.檢查清楚<span style=\"color: gold;\">附近係真係冇狗埋伏同支援</span>先好進攻<br />\n<br />\n5.一旦決定要進攻 就要<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一口氣衝或者行上去<br />\n千祈唔好向前行下又停下</span></strong></span> 咁樣只會令班狗有時間研究點樣對付你哋 所以一定要殺佢哋一個措手不及 唔比佢哋有時間反應<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6.<span style=\"color: gold;\">一切都要視乎當時環境同情況而決定</span><br />\n<br />\n香港人 報仇 再唔係一句口號 而係要行動 唔好再比班狗睇死我哋唔識進攻<br />\n<br />\n最後請各位安全至上 期待同你地喺煲底除罩相見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">如有更多建議 歡迎喺下邊提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:19:08.000Z","msg":"Push 勿戀陣地戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726209/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726209/page/1</a><br />\n深度分析，大家可以都睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3d6fbec5d0b1f160d59a1f5c37807f4f97855e","tid":1716114,"uid":104917,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"事實證明<br />\n勇武數量真係有限<br />\n對唔住我係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97cd2a566d7427277adceb6702b19349e2261c54","tid":1716114,"uid":198113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:53:06.000Z","msg":"Push